                    <h3>The Koch Curve</h3>
                    <p>
                        This spiky arrangement of equilateral triangles is the fifth step in the construction of a Koch curve fractal.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        The full fractal could pack a line of infinite length onto a space the size of this letter ‘l’.
                    </p>
